  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SGVisualExplorer
    This class allows you act as all of the agents in a stochastic game (controlled by a World object) by choosing actions for each of them to take in specific states.
    TextAreaStreams
    Object that provides an InputStream and OutputStream that affect the content of a JTextArea.
    VisualExplorer
    This class allows you act as the agent by choosing actions in an Environment.
